channel.title: Compiling error
channel.description:
When i tried to compile my server (I had to change the path from [code]@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_17\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause[/code] to [code] @echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_15\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause [/code]
I get this error... :( [code]Error occurred during initialization of VM Java/lang.noClassDefFoundError: Java/lang/Object[/code]
How do I fix? I changed that and the IP my client connects too. that's it
